# 🚀 Resume Ranking System (ATS)

An AI-powered **Resume Ranking System** that analyzes resumes and ranks candidates based on job description relevance.
The system helps recruiters quickly identify the most suitable candidates using **Automated ATS scoring**.

---

## 📌 Problem Statement

Recruiters face several challenges during the hiring process:

* Thousands of resumes for a single job
* Only **6 seconds average review time**
* Traditional ATS systems rely on **keyword matching**
* Qualified candidates are rejected due to missing exact keywords

This project solves the problem by using **semantic analysis and intelligent ranking**.

---

## 💡 Solution

The **Resume Ranking System** automatically analyzes resumes and compares them with the job description.

The system performs:

* Resume text extraction
* Skill identification
* Job description comparison
* ATS score calculation
* Candidate ranking

This helps recruiters quickly select the best candidates.

---

## ✨ Features

✔ Upload multiple resumes
✔ Extract text from resume files
✔ Compare resume with job description
✔ Generate ATS score
✔ Rank candidates based on relevance
✔ Admin dashboard
✔ Resume storage system

