## ⚙ Installation

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

git clone https://github.com/athirau820-droid/resume-ranking-system.git

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies

npm install

### 3️⃣ Run Backend

node server.js

### 4️⃣ Run Frontend

npm start

